headline: NextEra Energy Targets Data Center Demand With Nuclear And Carbon Capture
summary: NextEra Energy is working on power deals with major tech firms to support electricity hungry data centers. The company is exploring nuclear fleet expansion and record renewables additions to meet rising server load. NextEra is in advanced talks on a new gas power plant with carbon capture in partnership with ExxonMobil.
